	to TclEvalObjvInternal. [Bug 219362], fix by David Knoll.

2002-03-25  Jeff Hobbs  <jeffh@ActiveState.com>

	* generic/tclMain.c: reduced oversized static buffer allocation.

	* unix/Makefile.in: added shell and gdb targets

