	* unix/tcl.m4: backported 8.4 changes to HP-UX, IRIX64-6.*, SunOS,
	FreeBSD, AIX and Darwin targets.  Updated SC_LOADTCLCONFIG to
	detect when we build against a Tcl build dir.

